------------------------------------------------------------

Confirm:

- Python works in system terminal
- PyCharm interpreter is correct
- Python Console works
- Script runs
- pandas installs
- Data loads
- df.head() prints rows

If everything works, say:

"You are now ready to begin computational psychology."
